name: The First Date
description:
He picked the best flower he could find from the florist that lived in the neighborhood. Carefully wrapping it in cellophane, he stopped. It would be better to just hold it as he made his way to her. The petals of the flower were soft and delicate. Why cover it up with plastic? It was their first date and he was excited.
